import 'css-doodle'
import './App.css'
import React from 'react'
import Navigation from './Navigation'
import Calculator from './Calculator'
import cssDoodle from 'css-doodle'

function App () {
  return (
    <>
      <Navigation onclick={cssDoodle.update()}/>
      <Calculator />
    </>
  )
}

export default App
